{"data":[{"date":"19:07 20/06","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 20/6: Nh\u1edd thuy\u1ebft kh\u00e1ch MU s\u1eafp c\u00f3 \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d 100 tri\u1ec7u euro","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/20/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-206-nho-thuyet-khach-mu-sap-co-bom-tan-100-trieu-euro.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 20/6.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1edd thuy\u1ebft kh\u00e1ch MU s\u1eafp c\u00f3 \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d 100 tri\u1ec7u euro</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 206 MU s\u1eafp c\u00f3 bom t\u1ea5n 100 tri\u1ec7u euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 206 MU s\u1eafp c\u00f3 bom t\u1ea5n 100 tri\u1ec7u euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/matic.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU mu\u1ed1n Matic thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Milinkovic-Savic t\u1edbi Old Trafford</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM.U \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng Nemanja Matic s\u1ebd thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Sergej Milinkovic-Savic c\u1ee7a Lazio c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. Hi\u1ec7n b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y \u0111ang c\u00f9ng \u0110T Serbia tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>\"Tim Cahill c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p \u0110an M\u1ea1ch\"</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Stan Lazaridis ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Tim Cahill, c\u1ef1u sao \u0110T \u00dac tin r\u1eb1ng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 38 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2 b\u1ea3ng C.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec Asensio</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo El Gol Digital, MU, Chelsea v\u00e0 PSG l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Marco Asensio c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Sao tr\u1ebb tuy\u1ec3n Anh s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng thay th\u1ebf Dele Alli</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Loftus-Cheek s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng thay th\u1ebf Alli. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 22 tu\u1ed5i cho bi\u1ebft s\u1ebd th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n h\u1ebft kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Southgate tin t\u01b0\u1edfng x\u1ebfp \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Panama v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 24/6 t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Juventus \u0111\u00f2i 80 tri\u1ec7u euro cho Pjanic</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pjanic khang dinh chi trich Juventus la khong cong bang\" title=\"Pjanic kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Juventus l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/24/Man-City-muon-mua-Miralem-Pjanic-nhung-khong-thanh-cong-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Juventus ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Pjanic v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 80 tri\u1ec7u euro</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb Tuttosport kh\u1eb3ngd \u0111\u1ecbnh Juventus \u0111\u00f2i 80 tri\u1ec7u euro cho ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Miralem Pjanic, hi\u1ec7n Real, Barca v\u00e0 Chelsea l\u00e0 3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1t khao c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1990.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Arsenal s\u1eafp c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 3</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Sampdoria, Massimo Ferrero \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng Lucas Torreira s\u1eafp c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Arsenal v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u euro. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n Chelsea mua Mertens\u00a0</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Maurizio Sarri, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1eafp thay th\u1ebf Conte mu\u1ed1n Chelsea mua Dries Mertens \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, The Blues c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi 35 tri\u1ec7u euro cho ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Wilshere th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o r\u1eddi Arsenal</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jack Wilshere \u0111\u00e3 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o r\u1eb1ng anh s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Arsenal sau 17 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Emirates \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3737","checkdouble":"189083"},{"date":"02:53 21/06","title":"Ch\u00fac m\u1eebng Luis Suarez, c\u1ef1u sao MU ti\u1ec7n th\u1ec3 h\u00e9 l\u1ed9 l\u1eddi m\u1eddi gia nh\u1eadp Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/20/chuc-mung-luis-suarez-cuu-sao-mu-tien-the-he-lo-loi-moi-gia-nhap-barca.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 bi\u00ean Guillermo Varela cho bi\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e0n anh tr\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Uruguay \u0111\u00e3 tranh th\u1ee7 ch\u00e8o k\u00e9o anh v\u1ec1 c\u00f9ng s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh \u1edf s\u00e2n Camp Nou.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u01b0\u1ee3t qua ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng x\u00e9t tr\u00ean kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ai C\u1eadp, Luis Suarez ghi b\u00e0n tr\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-uruguay-vs-saudi-arabia-463-189080.html\" target=\"_blank\">Uruguay vs Saudi Arabia</span> \u0111\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c nh\u01b0ng v\u1eeba \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u1ef1u sao MU m\u1eebng Luis Suarez ghi b\u00e0n tr\u1eadn Uruguay vs Saudi Arabia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u1ef1u sao MU m\u1eebng Luis Suarez ghi b\u00e0n tr\u1eadn Uruguay vs Saudi Arabia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/Thong-ke-Uruguay-vs-Saudi-Arabia---Bang-A-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Luis Suarez ghi b\u00e0n tr\u1eadn Uruguay vs Saudi Arabia mang v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u00f2n g\u00ec \u00fd ngh\u0129a h\u01a1n khi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 31 tu\u1ed5i l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn ngay trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 100 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0110TQG. Ch\u00ednh b\u1edfi v\u1eady m\u00e0 anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Guillermo Varela n\u1ee9c n\u1edf ng\u1ee3i ca sau cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i 25 tu\u1ed5i t\u1eebng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Manchester United:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cLuis th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ea3 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Barcelona hay \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Uruguay. Nh\u1eefng g\u00ec anh \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0 \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 100 v\u00e0 ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0a n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 th\u1eb3ng ti\u1ebfn \u1edf World Cup, kh\u00f4ng g\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o h\u01a1n nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cLuis c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n anh th\u00e2n thi\u1ebft c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n n\u1eeda \u0111\u00f9a n\u1eeda th\u1eadt v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng nhau \u1edf c\u1ea5p CLB. Anh \u1ea5y c\u00f3 n\u00f3i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i v\u1ec1 Barca v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n, t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi d\u00e0nh cho t\u00f4i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00fac th\u00edch h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tr\u1ea3i qua 4 n\u0103m kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf Old Trafford, Varela tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 Penarol \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. Ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c, anh c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1ea7n tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Uruguay v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed chi\u1ebfm su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh World Cup 2018 \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i. Varela m\u01a1 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Barcelona, nh\u01b0ng anh c\u0169ng t\u1eebng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian \u0103n t\u1eadp c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb\u2026 Real Madrid.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-diem-nhan-sau-chien-thang-cua-uruguay-truoc-saudi-arabia-421-189108.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/nhung-diem-nhan-sau-chien-thang-cua-uruguay-truoc-saudi-arabia.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-diem-nhan-sau-chien-thang-cua-uruguay-truoc-saudi-arabia-421-189108.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Uruguay tr\u01b0\u1edbc Saudi Arabia</span><br>\r\nUruguay \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Saudi Arabia v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp. C\u00f9ng nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Uruguay vs...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3736","checkdouble":"189114"},{"date":"19:24 20/06","title":"MU nh\u1eafm sao kh\u1ee7ng tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/5/26/mu-nham-sao-khung-tuyen-duc-nang-cap-hang-thu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>MU mu\u1ed1n mua trung v\u1ec7 Jerome Boateng c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jerome Boateng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng r\u1eddi Bayern Munich</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m qua, trung v\u1ec7 Jerome Boateng l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich. Ng\u00f4i sao 29 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u danh hi\u1ec7u c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU mu\u1ed1n mua trung v\u1ec7 Jerome Boateng c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"MU mu\u1ed1n mua trung v\u1ec7 Jerome Boateng c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/22/MU-muon-mua-trung-ve-Jerome-Boateng-cua-Bayern-Munich-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>&nbsp;Jerome Boateng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Bayern Munich</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nSau 7 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi &ldquo;H\u00f9m x\u00e1m&rdquo; trung v\u1ec7 Jerome Boateng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nGi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh Karl-Heinz Rummenigge c\u1ee7a Bayern \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng Bayern Munich s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u1edf l\u1ea1i, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng m\u1ecdi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. N\u1ebfu Boateng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c n\u1eb7ng&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nPh\u00eda Bayern c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i, ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd Boateng s\u1ebd ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>M.U chi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Boateng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU mu\u1ed1n mua trung v\u1ec7 Jerome Boateng c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bayern Boateng\" title=\"Bayern Boateng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/9/18/Noi-bo-Bayern-luc-duc-vi-trung-ve-Jerome-Boateng-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU mu\u1ed1n mua Boateng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nMourinho \u0111ang r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p v\u1edbi Eric Bailly \u1edf trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n Chris Smalling ho\u1eb7c&nbsp;Phil Jones \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00f3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-dua-ra-quyet-dinh-cuoi-cung-vu-sao-khung-tottenham-172-188260.html\" target=\"_blank\">M.U quan t\u00e2m Alderweireld c\u1ee7a Tottenham</span>, song s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 Spurs \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn. Theo nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin, MU \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb b\u1ecf Alderweireld, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang Boateng c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nManchester Evening News kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Bayern \u0111\u00f2i 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, song v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Boateng \u0111\u00f2i ra \u0111i, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i chi t\u1ed1i \u0111a 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3735","checkdouble":"189082"},{"date":"19:36 20/06","title":"H\u00e0ng hot World Cup \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng cho \u0111\u1ea1i gia Premier League","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/hang-hot-world-cup-danh-tieng-cho-dai-gia-premier-league.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 ng\u1eafn g\u1ecdn c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi cha th\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Aleksandr Golovin c\u00e0ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean n\u00f3ng h\u01a1n sau k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 tr\u00ean qu\u00ea nh\u00e0.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga \u0111ang th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n di\u1ec7n m\u1ea1o \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f3 tin v\u1edbi hai chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Saudi Arabia v\u00e0 Ai C\u1eadp, qua \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua b\u1ea3ng A \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u00e0ng hot Golovin gia nh\u1eadp Premier League sau World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"H\u00e0ng hot Golovin gia nh\u1eadp Premier League sau World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/cska-tu-choi-ban-golovin-cho-juventus.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>H\u00e0ng hot Golovin gia nh\u1eadp Premier League sau World Cup 2018?</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Si\u00eau d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb Denis Cheryshev \u0111ang c\u00f9ng ng\u00f4i sao Cristiano Ronaldo d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u danh s\u00e1ch ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ea3 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, gi\u1edbi m\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec7u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eafc t\u00ean m\u1ed9t Aleksandr Golovin t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t trong ng\u00e0y khai m\u1ea1c t\u01b0ng m\u1eebng, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 22 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p hai \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o c\u00f9ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5m \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi Golovin l\u1ecdt m\u1eaft xanh c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i gia Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, \u0111i\u1ec1u th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra t\u1eeb g\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t n\u0103m nay. C\u00f2n nh\u1edb h\u1ed3i h\u00e8 2017, Arsenal t\u1eebng ti\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a t\u00e0i n\u0103ng CSKA Moscow nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. Gi\u1edd, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh nh\u01b0 h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i nh\u1eadn tin m\u1eebng c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 tham v\u1ecdng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 h\u00e0ng hot World Cup 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n cha c\u1ee7a Golovin \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i th\u1ebf n\u00e0y: \u201cCon trai t\u00f4i c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfn m\u1edbi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a n\u00f3. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Sasha \u0111ang b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u h\u1ecdc ti\u1ebfng Anh r\u1ed3i, n\u00f3 t\u1ecf r\u1ea5t h\u0103ng say r\u00e8n luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 trau d\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea5y.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng h\u01a1n minh ch\u1ee9ng cho d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh mu\u1ed1n th\u1eed s\u1ee9c \u1edf Premier League c\u1ee7a Golovin. Tuy nhi\u00ean, nh\u1eefng Arsenal hay Man Utd c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i nhanh ch\u00f3ng x\u00fac ti\u1ebfn n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t ng\u00f4i sao n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga v\u1ec1 tay Juventus. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/chu-nha-nga-dai-thang-tran-khai-mac-world-cup-2018-take-that-hoi-the-gioi-421-188544.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/chu-nha-nga-dai-thang-tran-khai-mac-world-cup-2018-take-that-hoi-the-gioi.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/chu-nha-nga-dai-thang-tran-khai-mac-world-cup-2018-take-that-hoi-the-gioi-421-188544.html\">Ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga \u0111\u1ea1i th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn khai m\u1ea1c World Cup 2018: Take That, h\u1ee1i th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi!</span><br>\r\nBu\u1ed5i l\u1ec5 khai m\u1ea1c World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a nam danh ca Robbie Williams, c\u1ef1u th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh c\u1ee7a nh\u00f3m nh\u1ea1c huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Take That. Take That, nh\u1eadn l\u1ea5y n\u00e0y! - \u0110\u00f3...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3734","checkdouble":"189086"},{"date":"20:31 20/06","title":"\u0110\u00e2y! Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Liverpool","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/20/day-thu-mon-moi-nhat-lot-vao-tam-ngam-cua-liverpool.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Nick Pope c\u1ee7a Burnley, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Anfield ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 26 tu\u1ed5i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Liverpool t\u1eeb b\u1ecf Alisson</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLiverpool \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Karius, ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u sau khi m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft C1 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Nick Pope c\u1ee7a Burnley h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Nick Pope c\u1ee7a Burnley h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/24/Liverpool-muon-mua-Nick-Pope-cua-Burnley-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool t\u1eeb b\u1ecf Alisson</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nThe Kop \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson c\u1ee7a Roma nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t Serie A m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra t\u1edbi 45 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y, song Roma h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 t\u1edbi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1o ch\u00ed T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/chi-tiet-hop-dong-alisson-sap-ky-voi-real-madrid-180-188633.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Alisson</span>, h\u1ecd b\u1ecf ra 70 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n. Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 sau khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh ngh\u0129a v\u1ee5 c\u00f9ng \u0110T Brazil \u1edf World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang Pope</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Nick Pope c\u1ee7a Burnley, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Anfield ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 26 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"thu mon Nick Pope\" title=\"thu mon Nick Pope\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/20/day-thu-mon-moi-nhat-lot-vao-tam-ngam-cua-liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool chi 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Nick Pope</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n sinh n\u0103m 1992 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t, anh g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn gi\u00fap Burnley c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 7 tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPope \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi 12/35 l\u1ea7n \u1edf Premier League, anh gi\u00fap h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Burnley tr\u00e1nh kh\u1ecfi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n thua.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBurnley ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, song Liverpool \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 h\u1ecd d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh chi ra s\u1ebd thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Burnley nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Pope, Liverpool c\u00f2n nh\u1eafm \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Jack Butland c\u1ee7a Stoke City, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 25 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng c\u00f9ng Stoke v\u00e0 \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bet365 \u0111\u00f2i 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3733","checkdouble":"189087"},{"date":"21:05 20/06","title":"\"HLV Sarri s\u1ebd thay \u0111\u1ed5i Chelsea\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/31/hlv-sarri-se-thay-doi-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kalidou Koulibaly ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Maurizio Sarri, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Napoli tin t\u01b0\u1edfng \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y c\u0169 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Chelsea gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sarri s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m thay th\u1ebf Conte</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, HLV Conte kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Chelsea c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trong Top 4 t\u1ea1i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. Vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ec9 x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 5 v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 Champions League khi\u1ebfn BL\u0110 v\u00e0 NHM \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kalidou Koulibaly ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Maurizio Sarri h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Kalidou Koulibaly ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Maurizio Sarri h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/31/hlv-sarri-se-thay-doi-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Maurizio Sarri s\u1eafp ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng v\u1eady vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn Conte \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi Chelsea. \u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin cho r\u1eb1ng The Blues quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sa th\u1ea3i \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec1n b\u00f9 vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Conte, Maurizio Sarri l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London. \u00d4ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chia tay Napoli \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin, Sarri \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf Anh, d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn \u00f4ng s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 58 tu\u1ed5i k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 3 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Chelsea v\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng 5 tri\u1ec7u euro/m\u00f9a.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Koulibaly tin Sarri th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf Chelsea</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kalidou Koulibaly ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Maurizio Sarri, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Napoli tin t\u01b0\u1edfng \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y c\u0169 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Chelsea gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"hau ve Koulibaly\" title=\"hau ve Koulibaly\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/10/6/chu-tich-napoli-tiet-lo-gia-khung-chelsea-moi-chao-de-co-koulibaly.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Koulibaly tin Sarri s\u1ebd th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi Sarri r\u1eddi Napoli, \u00f4ng \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t HLV t\u1ed1t. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft \u00f4ng \u1ea5y s\u1ebd d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o, t\u00f4i th\u1ea5y nhi\u1ec1u tin \u0111\u1ed3n cho r\u1eb1ng \u00f4ng \u1ea5y s\u1ebd d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Sarri ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.\u201d</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\"T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng \u00f4ng \u1ea5y s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u danh hi\u1ec7u v\u1edbi Chelsea, v\u1edbi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u00f4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c gi\u00fap Chelsea mang v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Chelsea, Koulibaly kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: \u201cT\u00f4i c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Napoli v\u00e0 t\u00f4i t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. M\u1ecdi th\u00f4ng tin li\u00ean\u00a0quan \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3732","checkdouble":"189088"},{"date":"03:40 21/06","title":"T\u00e2n binh g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn Arsenal v\u00ec c\u1ea3 Wenger v\u00e0 Emery","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/20/tan-binh-gac-den-lua-chon-arsenal-vi-hlv-emery.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Bernd Leno ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Arsenal trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Arsenal d\u01b0\u1edbi tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i m\u1edbi Unai Emery m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Bernd Leno t\u1eeb Bayer Leverkusen trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, CLB th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e3 chi 22 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 26 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 5 n\u0103m v\u1edbi anh.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u00e2n binh m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o Th\u1ee7 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u chia s\u1ebb \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o m\u1edbi. Theo \u0111\u00f3, Leno ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gia nh\u1eadp Arsenal ch\u1ec9 qua m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i v\u1edbi Emery, t\u00e2n HLV c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 m\u1edbi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Emirates trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Bernd Leno gia nh\u1eadp Arsenal v\u00ec Wenger v\u00e0 Emery h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Bernd Leno gia nh\u1eadp Arsenal v\u00ec Wenger v\u00e0 Emery h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/tan-binh-gac-den-lua-chon-arsenal-vi-hlv-emery.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Bernd Leno gia nh\u1eadp Arsenal v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 22 tri\u1ec7u Euro</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Anh n\u00f3i: \u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t fan h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Arsenal, ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu l\u00e0 v\u00ec Arsene Wenger sau nh\u1eefng g\u00ec v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i m\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, \u00f4ng \u1ea5y c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ra \u0111i nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng vi\u1ebft n\u00ean trang s\u1eed m\u1edbi.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cGi\u1edd ch\u00fang ta c\u0169ng c\u00f3 Unai Emery, m\u1ed9t HLV t\u00e0i n\u0103ng kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m c\u1ea1nh g\u00ec. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n qua \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i v\u1edbi \u00f4ng \u1ea5y v\u00e0 hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1eb1ng \u00f4ng \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, v\u1eady n\u00ean t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc, l\u01b0\u1ee1ng l\u1ef1 v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gia nh\u1eadp Arsenal.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Bernd Leno n\u0103m nay 26 tu\u1ed5i tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh t\u1eeb l\u00f2 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Stuttgart, sau \u0111\u00f3 gia nh\u1eadp Leverkusen n\u0103m 2011 v\u00e0 \u0111ang gi\u1eef k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n tr\u1ebb nh\u1ea5t ra s\u00e2n \u1edf Champions League (19 tu\u1ed5i 193 ng\u00e0y) trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Chelsea. 7 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u1edf BayArena, anh \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea5n gi\u1eef khung g\u1ed7 trong 304 tr\u1eadn tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Leno \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2015 v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 6 l\u1ea7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Mannschaft, tham d\u1ef1 v\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Confederations Cup 2017 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch World Cup 2018. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Bernd Leno l\u00e0 t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 hai c\u1ee7a Arsenal trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh Stephan Lichtsteiner t\u1eeb Juventus theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/clb-arsenal-chinh-thuc-trinh-lang-tan-binh-thu-hai-trong-he-2018-172-188980.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/clb-arsenal-chinh-thuc-trinh-lang-tan-binh-thu-hai-trong-he-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/clb-arsenal-chinh-thuc-trinh-lang-tan-binh-thu-hai-trong-he-2018-172-188980.html\">CLB Arsenal CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0ng t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 hai trong h\u00e8 2018</span><br>\r\nCLB Arsenal m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1ee9 hai trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c Bernd Leno \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Bayer Leverkusen.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3731","checkdouble":"189113"},{"date":"12:56 20/06","title":"Hai con trai c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Pique m\u1eb7c \u00e1o c\u1ed5 v\u0169 tuy\u1ec3n Colombia","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/hai-con-trai-cua-trung-ve-pique-mac-ao-co-vu-tuyen-colombia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00e1c qu\u00fd t\u1eed c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Milan v\u00e0 Sasha, m\u1eb7c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh Milan v\u00e0 Sasha di\u1ec7n \u00e1o m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1eb9 Shakira \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i tr\u00ean trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n. B\u1ea1n g\u00e1i c\u1ee7a Pique mang qu\u1ed1c t\u1ecbch Colombia v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u01b0 t\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha t\u1eeb nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m nay. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 d\u1ecbp hi\u1ebfm hoi ca s\u0129 nh\u1ea1c latin khoe \u1ea3nh hai c\u1eadu nh\u00f3c ba v\u00e0 5 tu\u1ed5i. Nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1eafc m\u1eafc: \"Shakira c\u00f3 l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 khi tuy\u1ec3n T\u00e2y Ban Nha thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y mai kh\u00f4ng\".<br />\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hai con trai Pique m\u1eb7c \u00e1o c\u1ed5 v\u0169 tuy\u1ec3n Colombia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Hai con trai Pique m\u1eb7c \u00e1o c\u1ed5 v\u0169 tuy\u1ec3n Colombia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/cc-1427-1529456960.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Hai con Pique m\u1eb7c \u00e1o c\u1ed5 v\u0169 tuy\u1ec3n Colombia - qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a m\u1eb9 Shakira. \u1ea2nh: NS.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nNh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a hai con trai Pique - Shakira, tuy\u1ec3n Colombia b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u1ec3 thua Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n 1-2 \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 m\u1ea5t ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eeb s\u1edbm sau th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf v\u00f4 duy\u00ean v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eafng tay tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ch\u00e2u \u00c1. Shakira kh\u00f4ng t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Mordovia Arena \u1edf Nga \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp theo d\u00f5i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00ec c\u00f4 \u0111ang trong chuy\u1ebfn l\u01b0u di\u1ec5n \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. Ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u1edf nhi\u1ec1u qu\u1ed1c gia b\u1ecb ho\u00e3n g\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t n\u0103m v\u00ec v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe c\u1ee7a Shakira.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nN\u1eef ho\u00e0ng nh\u1ea1c latin l\u00e0 fan cu\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00f4n th\u1ec3 thao vua. C\u00f4 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt l\u1ea7n t\u1edbi s\u00e2n c\u1ed5 v\u0169 cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng Colombia. Shakira c\u0169ng n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi b\u00e0i h\u00e1t \"Waka Waka\" t\u1ea1i World Cup 2010. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Nga b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u, b\u1ea1n g\u00e1i Pique c\u0169ng tham d\u1ef1 v\u00e0 bi\u1ec3u di\u1ec5n trong bu\u1ed5i l\u1ec5 chia tay \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Colombia l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSau khi ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh chuy\u1ebfn l\u01b0u di\u1ec5n, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Shakira \u0111\u01b0a hai qu\u00fd t\u1eed t\u1edbi Nga \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ed5 v\u0169 Pique, tuy\u1ec3n T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Colombia n\u1ebfu hai \u0111\u1ed9i l\u1ecdt s\u00e2u v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng trong.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3730","checkdouble":"189031"},{"date":"14:35 20/06","title":"\"H\u1ecda s\u0129 ti\u00ean tri\" World Cup 2018 n\u1ed5i nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean MXH v\u00ec ... ph\u00e1n sai","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/hoa-si-tien-tri-world-cup-2018-noi-nhat-tren-mxh-vi-phan-sai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1ed9t khi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111en \u0111\u1ee7i m\u00e0 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o m\u1eaft xanh, t\u1ea1o c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ec3 \"th\u00e1nh\" s\u00e1ng t\u00e1c tranh ch\u00e2n dung, th\u00ec d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee1 n\u00e0o, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 l\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 h\u01a1n 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n thua tan n\u00e1t...</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00e0o l\u01b0u ti\u00ean tri tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 t\u1eeb 2010 khi World Cup \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i Nam Phi v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00fa b\u1ea1ch tu\u1ed9c n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi - Paul. Paul n\u0103m \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c 100% k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 7 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy v\u1eady, b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nh\u1eefng nh\u00e0 ti\u00ean tri l\u1ed7i l\u1ea1c v\u1edbi x\u00e1c xu\u1ea5t d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c cao, v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u00f3 c\u00e1c &quot;th\u00e1nh ti\u00ean tri&quot; kh\u00e1c c\u0169ng n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m, nh\u01b0ng l\u00e0 b\u1edfi si\u00eau n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c &quot;\u0111o\u00e1n to\u00e0n sai&quot; c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. N\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng nh\u1ea5t \u1edf m\u1ea3ng n\u00e0y c\u00f3 l\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ai kh\u00e1c ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 Vua b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Pele. B\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Pele \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao th\u00ec th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7...<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed s\u00f4i s\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a WC 2018, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y d\u00e2n m\u1ea1ng l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phen x\u00f4n xao truy\u1ec1n tay nhau c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a &quot;th\u00e1nh ti\u00ean tri World Cup 2018&quot; tr\u00ean MXH. Nguy\u1ec5n Minh \u0110\u1ee9c y\u00eau b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u00e0 c\u00f3 t\u00e0i v\u1ebd ch\u00e2n dung, nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed7i khi anh ch\u00e0ng vung c\u1ecd v\u1ebd c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o, th\u00ec y nh\u01b0 r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1ea5y s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea3m h\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u00e1nh ti\u00ean tri World Cup 2018 tr\u00ean MXH V\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed9i n\u00e0o, \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00f3 thua h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u00e1nh ti\u00ean tri World Cup 2018 tr\u00ean MXH V\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed9i n\u00e0o, \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00f3 thua h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/354050316363903333794507548367927087464448o-15294688824611035461980.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ch\u00e2n dung Messi (Nguy\u1ec5n Minh \u0110\u1ee9c)</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;N\u00f3i c\u00f3 s\u00e1ch, m\u00e1ch c\u00f3 ch\u1ee9ng&quot;, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u1ecdt m\u1eaft xanh c\u1ee7a Minh \u0110\u1ee9c l\u00e0 si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina Lionel Messi. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, b\u1ee9c ch\u00e2n dung \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Minh \u0110\u1ee9c chia s\u1ebb l\u00ean trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n k\u00e8m d\u00f2ng caption: &quot;Anh em x\u00f4ng l\u00ean!&quot;. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ngay sau \u0111\u00f3, Messi thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng qu\u1ea3 penalty, Argen ho\u00e0 nh\u1ea1t nho\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland, \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 y\u1ebfu h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u!<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u00e1ng n\u00f3i n\u1ebfu \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c v\u1ebd... B\u1edfi ngay sau \u0111\u00f3, si\u00eau n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a &quot;th\u00e1nh ti\u00ean tri&quot; n\u00e0y ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1edbi b\u1ee9c ch\u00e2n dung danh th\u1ee7 Neymar tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Brazil g\u1eb7p Thu\u1ef5 S\u0129. V\u00e0 nh\u01b0 ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft, Neymar c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed3i, Brazil - \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean s\u1ed1 1 cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch h\u00f2a \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 1 - 1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb s\u1ee9 s\u1edf \u0110\u1ed3ng H\u1ed3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chan dung Neymar (Anh FB Nguyen Minh Duc)\" title=\"Ch\u00e2n dung Neymar (\u1ea2nh FB Nguy\u1ec5n Minh \u0110\u1ee9c)\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/screen-shot-2018-06-20-at-114030-am-1529469656652950322287.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ch\u00e2n dung Neymar (\u1ea2nh FB Nguy\u1ec5n Minh \u0110\u1ee9c)</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ee9c v\u1ebd th\u1ee9 3 \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u0103ng l\u00ean trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 y\u00eau m\u1ebfn d\u00e0nh cho \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c. Tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, c\u00e1c oppa thua 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Thu\u1ef5 \u0110i\u1ec3n gi\u00e0 nua.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chan dung Heung-min Sun (Anh FB Nguyen Minh Duc)\" title=\"Ch\u00e2n dung Heung-min Sun (\u1ea2nh FB Nguy\u1ec5n Minh \u0110\u1ee9c)\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/screen-shot-2018-06-20-at-114247-am-15294697897562016298991.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ch\u00e2n dung Heung-min Sun (\u1ea2nh FB Nguy\u1ec5n Minh \u0110\u1ee9c)</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ti\u1ebfp theo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Minh \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1ebd ch\u00e2n dung l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao Colombia James Rodriguez - c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2014. \u0110\u1ec9nh \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 \u0111en \u0111\u1ee7i l\u00e0 ngay t\u1eeb ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 4, Colombia \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi 10 ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n thua \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m, c\u00f9ng chi\u1ebfc th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf c\u1ee7a Carlos Sanchez. Cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn, Colombia thua Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n 1-2.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chan dung James Rodriguez (Anh FB Nguyen Minh Duc)\" title=\"Ch\u00e2n dung James Rodriguez (\u1ea2nh FB Nguy\u1ec5n Minh \u0110\u1ee9c)\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/screen-shot-2018-06-20-at-115055-am-15294702727381491470173.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ch\u00e2n dung James Rodriguez (\u1ea2nh FB Nguy\u1ec5n Minh \u0110\u1ee9c)</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;N\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n&quot; m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a &quot;th\u00e1nh ti\u00ean tri&quot; l\u00e0 si\u00eau sao Mohamed Salah c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ai C\u1eadp. T\u1ed1i qua, Minh \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1ebd ch\u00e2n dung Salah v\u00e0 \u0111\u0103ng l\u00ean trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n th\u00ec trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng nay, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 Salah \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i WC t\u1eeb c\u00fa penalty c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Ai C\u1eadp tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1eadn thua th\u1ea3m 1-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cha dung Mohamed Salah (Anh FB Nguyen Minh Duc)\" title=\"Ch\u00e2 dung Mohamed Salah (\u1ea2nh FB Nguy\u1ec5n Minh \u0110\u1ee9c)\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/screen-shot-2018-06-20-at-115606-am-1529470581494730442215.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ch\u00e2n dung Mohamed Salah (\u1ea2nh FB Nguy\u1ec5n Minh \u0110\u1ee9c)</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n th\u00fa v\u1ecb c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng b\u1ee9c ch\u00e2n dung \u0111\u1eb9p xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc sau khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chia s\u1ebb \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c g\u00e2y ch\u00fa \u00fd v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn d\u00e2n m\u1ea1ng v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng th\u00edch th\u00fa, qua \u0111\u00f3 nh\u1eadn v\u1ec1 h\u00e0ng ngh\u00ecn l\u01b0\u1ee3t like ch\u1ec9 trong m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian ng\u1eafn. \u0110a s\u1ed1 c\u01b0 d\u00e2n m\u1ea1ng t\u1ecf ra n\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u1ebd ch\u00e2n dung c\u00f9ng si\u00eau n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c &quot;\u00e1m qu\u1ebb&quot; Minh \u0110\u1ee9c. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, nhi\u1ec1u d\u00e2n m\u1ea1ng t\u1ecf ra lo l\u1eafng v\u00e0 n\u0103n n\u1ec9 &quot;thanh ti\u00ean tri&quot; n\u00e0y \u0111\u1eebng mang ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u00ecnh y\u00eau th\u00edch ra v\u1ebd v\u00ec lo l\u1eafng th\u1ea3m ho\u1ea1 s\u1ebd x\u1ea3y \u0111\u1ebfn...</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo kenh14.vn<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3729","checkdouble":"189044"},{"date":"15:14 20/06","title":"Ca s\u0129 Colombia b\u1ecb tr\u1ed9m tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u00f4 khi \u0111\u1ebfn Nga xem World Cup 2018","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/ca-si-colombia-bi-trom-trieu-do-khi-den-nga-xem-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"${8_news_content2}","new_url":"","id":"3728","checkdouble":"189051"},{"date":"15:38 20/06","title":"Hotgirl \"ng\u1ee7 g\u1eadt\" g\u00e2y b\u00e3o tr\u00ean truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/20/hotgirl-ngu-gat-gay-bao-tren-truyen-hinh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ee7y Ti\u00ean l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1ea1ng s\u0103n \u0111\u00f3n nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t sau ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh \"N\u00f3ng c\u00f9ng World Cup\" \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng tr\u00ean VTV nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y v\u1eeba qua.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Trong d\u00e0n Hot girl xinh \u0111\u1eb9p c\u1ee7a \"N\u00f3ng c\u00f9ng World Cup\", Th\u1ee7y Ti\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n cho \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n V\u1edbi v\u1ebb ngo\u00e0i xinh x\u1eafn \u0111\u00e1ng y\u00eau c\u00f9ng th\u00e2n h\u00ecnh n\u00f3ng b\u1ecfng \"chu\u1ea9n kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ec9nh\", Th\u1ee7y Ti\u00ean l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u khen ng\u1ee3i t\u1eeb c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1ea1ng<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, trong ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh ghi h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh c\u00f9ng World Cup, Th\u1ee7y Ti\u00ean c\u00f2n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u00e2y \"s\u1ed1t\" b\u1eb1ng b\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh ng\u1ee7 g\u1eadt ngay t\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1eddng quay c\u1ee7a VTV<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Th\u1ee7y Ti\u00ean c\u0169ng t\u1eebng khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u ch\u00e0ng trai m\u00ea m\u1ea9n khi b\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh c\u00f4 m\u1eb7c \u00e1o d\u00e0i tr\u1eafng ng\u1ee7 g\u1eadt ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1eddng. Bi\u1ec7t danh hot girl \"ng\u1ee7 g\u1eadt\" v\u00ec th\u1ebf \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t cho Th\u1ee7y Ti\u00ean<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i \u0111\u1eddi, Th\u1ee7y Ti\u00ean c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u00f4 g\u00e1i c\u00f3 phong c\u00e1ch \u0103n m\u1eb7c r\u1ea5t b\u1eaft m\u1eaft. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u00e2n h\u00ecnh n\u00f3ng b\u1ecfng, Th\u1ee7y Ti\u00ean c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec3u bi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 khi xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh c\u00f9ng World Cup<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/ngam-ve-dep-nong-bong-goi-cam-cua-hot-girl-doi-tuyen-nhat-ban-6.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/ngam-ve-dep-nong-bong-goi-cam-cua-hot-girl-doi-tuyen-nhat-ban-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/bia.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\